Flappy Bird Reborn is an exciting game available as a Chrome extension. It is a revamped version of the popular game "Flappy Bird." In this game, players control a small bird and navigate it through a series of obstacles by tapping on the screen to make the bird flap its wings and gain altitude. The objective is to achieve the highest score possible by successfully maneuvering through the gaps between the pipes without colliding with them.

The game "Flappy Bird Reborn" captures the addictive and challenging gameplay of the original game while adding some new elements. It features vibrant graphics and smooth controls, providing an immersive and enjoyable gaming experience. Players can test their reflexes and concentration as they strive to beat their own high scores and compete with friends.

You can play "Flappy Bird Reborn" for free on the website https://monkeymart.org/. Simply visit the website and look for the game to start playing. Have fun and see how far you can guide the flappy bird!
